flowchart LR
    A[Collection] --> B[Purpose and Notice]
    B --> C[Use]
    C --> D[Storage]
    D --> E[Access]
    E --> F[Third-Party Processing]
    F --> G[Logging and Monitoring]
    G --> H[Retention]
    H --> I[Deletion or Archiving]
    I --> J[Evidence and Accountability]

    A --> R1[Risk: unnecessary or unclear collection]
    D --> R2[Risk: inconsistent field-level safeguards]
    E --> R3[Risk: access beyond operational need]
    F --> R4[Risk: unclear vendor processing boundary]
    G --> R5[Risk: incomplete access traceability]
    H --> R6[Risk: undefined retention rules]
    J --> R7[Risk: weak evidence traceability]

    R1 --> P1[PIPEDA lens: Identifying Purposes, Limiting Collection]
    R2 --> P2[PIPEDA lens: Safeguards]
    R3 --> P3[PIPEDA lens: Accountability, Safeguards]
    R4 --> P4[PIPEDA lens: Accountability, Openness]
    R5 --> P5[PIPEDA lens: Accountability, Challenging Compliance]
    R6 --> P6[PIPEDA lens: Limiting Use, Disclosure, and Retention]
    R7 --> P7[PIPEDA lens: Accountability]
